Author: IdontwannadieordoI
Text: Thats not how it works.  You can have an eating disorder at any weight and binging when anorexic is pretty ""normal"" and in the long term inevitable. I am sure you could explain what happened to your doctor and let him make the judgement mate dont let your emotions get the best of you. The fact that going over your limit upsets you so much indicates an eating disorder on its own
